<Layout title="Privacy Policy - TopOnlineForm">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white p-6 md:p-10 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-t-4 border-red-600">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 border-b pb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">
      <p>
        At <strong>TopOnlineForm.com</strong>, the privacy of our visitors is of extreme importance to us. This Privacy Policy document outlines the types of personal information is received and collected by us and how it is used.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-bold text-black mt-2">Log Files</h3>
      <p>
        Like many other Web sites, TopOnlineForm.com makes use of log files. The information inside the log files includes internet protocol ( IP ) addresses, type of browser, Internet Service Provider ( ISP ), date/time stamp, referring/exit pages, and number of clicks to analyze trends.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-bold text-black mt-2">Cookies and Web Beacons</h3>
      <p>
        TopOnlineForm.com does use cookies to store information about visitors preferences, record user-specific information on which pages the user access or visit.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-bold text-black mt-2">DoubleClick DART Cookie</h3>
      <p>
        Google, as a third party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads on TopOnlineForm.com. Google's use of the DART cookie enables it to serve ads to users based on their visit to TopOnlineForm.com and other sites on the Internet.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
